        <div class="comment">
        <p class="metadata">Posted by Liber Chen (liber) on 2008-12-15T00:58:20.000+0000</p> 
        <div class="body">
            <p>It is not consistent.</p>

<p>Please consider below situation:</p>

<p>$a-&gt;setWeekDay(7);</p>

<p>$b = $a-&gt;toArray();
$weekDay = $b['weekday'];</p>

<p>echo $weekDay (It is 0, not 7)</p>

<hr /><p>But if it is consistent.
Then we can define a constant to check it.</p>

<p>define('SUNDAY', 0);  ( Or 7 if ISO standard)</p>

<p>$a-&gt;setWeekDay(SUNDAY);
$b = $a-&gt;toArray();
$weekDay = $b['weekday'];</p>

<p>echo $weekDay==SUNDAY (This will be true, because it is consistent)</p>

